11
00:00:59,620 --> 00:01:00,680
I specially chose a character

12
00:01:01,740 --> 00:01:04,600
from your and Jiang's names.

13
00:01:05,290 --> 00:01:06,320
I swore

14
00:01:07,280 --> 00:01:09,590
they will definitely pay the price.

15
00:01:13,920 --> 00:01:15,940
I will only do one thing from now on,

16
00:01:17,680 --> 00:01:18,970
