40
00:02:17,180 --> 00:02:18,380
Criminal Investigation Unit.

41
00:02:18,700 --> 00:02:19,540
Got it.

42
00:02:19,900 --> 00:02:20,860
Don't worry.

43
00:02:21,180 --> 00:02:22,300
In case something happens,

44
00:02:22,770 --> 00:02:24,100
I'll raise

45
