144
00:07:02,300 --> 00:07:04,260
Strive to see them soon.

145
00:07:08,050 --> 00:07:09,500
Bao is wrongfully accused.

146
00:07:11,780 --> 00:07:13,180
It wasn't me who helped Sun Changhai escape

147
00:07:13,660 --> 00:07:16,100
and killed Wu Ajin and Dian Lao'er.

148
00:07:16,780 --> 00:07:19,220
Tu Manjiang threatened me with Hui and our kid,

149
00:07:20,580 --> 00:07:22,180
