152
00:07:27,140 --> 00:07:28,780
That's all I know.

153
00:07:34,900 --> 00:07:35,740
Hello?

154
00:07:35,940 --> 00:07:36,780
Bin.

155
00:07:37,020 --> 00:07:37,900
I have found them.

156
00:07:38,260 --> 00:07:39,100
Send me the location.

157
00:07:39,300 --> 00:07:40,980
Ok.

158
00:07:42,860 --> 00:07:43,700
