164
00:08:05,060 --> 00:08:05,900
and discuss something

165
00:08:06,740 --> 00:08:07,580
with him.

166
00:08:08,820 --> 00:08:09,740
Please do me this favor, ok?

167
00:08:52,340 --> 00:08:53,460
A buddy of mine

168
00:08:55,580 --> 00:08:57,140
