174
00:09:11,140 --> 00:09:13,660
How should I settle this with you?

175
00:09:16,060 --> 00:09:16,900
Let me tell you,

176
00:09:17,780 --> 00:09:19,540
I didn't bring my people here today

177
00:09:20,220 --> 00:09:21,540
and didn't call the police either.

178
00:09:22,380 --> 00:09:24,220
I ran all the way to come here.

179
00:09:25,300 --> 00:09:26,300
I think

180
00:09:26,300 --> 00:09:27,980
you

181
00:09:28,530 --> 00:09:30,550
are worth me making this trip

182
00:09:31,210 --> 00:09:32,050
and having a talk nicely.

183
00:09:33,460 --> 00:09:34,940
Since you put it that way,

184
00:09:36,460 --> 00:09:37,820
let's have a chat.

185
00:09:38,820 --> 00:09:40,660
You're someone who follows the rules.

186
00:09:47,940 --> 00:09:48,780
Come with me.

187
00:09:54,980 --> 00:09:56,020
You wait for me in the car.

188
00:10:24,740 --> 00:10:25,580
Bao.

189
00:10:40,340 --> 00:10:41,300
Are you ok?

190
00:10:41,850 --> 00:10:42,820
Zheng Haotian

191
00:10:44,600 --> 00:10:45,440
