203
00:11:20,820 --> 00:11:22,020
But I have his phone number.

204
00:11:28,500 --> 00:11:29,420
Let me take a picture.

205
00:11:32,060 --> 00:11:32,900
Ok.

206
00:11:35,900 --> 00:11:37,300
I do have one request for you.

207
00:11:39,580 --> 00:11:42,380
Where are that guy surnamed Qi

208
00:11:43,860 --> 00:11:45,140
